<A>__{he leads her down through the stairwell of the large walk up. she follows him step by step. suddenly he pulls her into the corner of a doorway. wrapping the tablecloth around them, they melt into darkness. beneath the wrap, he puts his hand over her mouth and nose stopping her breath. outside after a long beat a ninja's foot silently glides past, climbing the stairs. inside he releases her nose. before she can finish taking a breath he yanks her up and they quickly descend the remaining stairs.}
